<item>
            <title>[LU-2773] remote directories cannot be removed by &quot;rm -r&quot;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2773</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;With MDSCOUNT=2, sanity test 31f will fail when the test creates a directory using &apos;lfs setdirstripe -i 1&apos; but then tries to remove it using &apos;rm -r&apos;. A test_rmdir function could be added to test-framework.sh to handle this case.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="17482">LU-2773</key>
            <summary>remote directories cannot be removed by &quot;rm -r&quot;</summary>
